# UnderwriteMe API
UnderwriteMe API is a set of REST endpoints which allows you to interact with underwriting workflow which consists of following components:

  * Application
  * Enquiry
  * Quote
  * Basket
  * Activation

# Group Application
Notes related resources of the **Application API**

## New Application [/application]
Creating new Application based on sent Customers and Products JSON data. 

### Create new Application [POST]
+ Request (application/json)

            {
                "customers":[
                    {
                        "id":"cus-001",
                        "name":"John",
                        "surname":"Doe",
                        "title":"MR",
                        "gender":"MALE",
                        "dateOfBirth":"1980-01-01",
                        "smoker":false,
                        "email":"john.doe@domain.com"
                    }
                ],
                "products":[
                    {
                        "type":"WHOLE_OF_LIFE",
                        "coverAmount":100000,
